  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">The Bottom Line</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      Compliance requirements should drive platform selection as much as learning features. If you need SCORM/xAPI support, regulatory audit trails, or HIPAA compliance, your options narrow quickly to enterprise platforms (Docebo, Absorb, TalentLMS) or LearnWorlds for smaller operations. For certification programs without complex eLearning standards, Thinkific and LearnWorlds offer excellent certificate management. Always verify compliance claims with your legal and security teams — platform marketing and actual certification capabilities can differ significantly.
    </p>
  </section>

